original_title: Gary Numan: Moogfest 2016, Day 2 - The Pleasure Principle
overview: At Moogfest 2016, held May 19-22, 2016 in Durham, NC, Gary Numan and his band performed three shows, to standing-room-only audiences. In his Thursday-Saturday night residency at Moogfest, Numan featured one of his classic albums each night: Replicas, The Pleasure Principle, and Telekon.
title: Gary Numan: Moogfest 2016, Day 2 - The Pleasure Principle
